 A = aI + bJ 
 A = \left[ \matrix{a & -b \\ b & a} \right], 
 I = \left[ \matrix{1 & 0 \\ 0 & 1} \right] \quad \text{and} \quad J = \left[ \matrix{0 & -1 \\ 1 & 0} \right]. 
